Because you can help someone now

MVP:
  What is the tragedy
    -the name of the tragedy
    -the type of the tragedy (fire, overflow, landslip, shooting, aircraft accident, etc.)

  Where is the tragedy
    -The City/State
    -Address

  Who are the victims of the tragedy
    -links to news with the name of the victims

  What they need and where they receive it
  List of news about the tragedy

  Looking for someone I care
    -Name, picture, contact. details

